Firestrike hangs on for his life, a grin from the battle consantly on 
his face.  As he sees maximal city come at him he swings forward, 
but misjudges the speed as he hits the top of a building and 
topples end over end across it.  "Thats it. " he yells at Prowl.  (I 
presume he kept flying and didn't crash into the building also)

Bringing his hand down beside his leg, he gestured,  The leg opend 
and a large cannon protruded out.  He brought it up level towards 
Prowl.  The qucikly puleld it straight down pointing it at the roof.  
Pulling the trigger a large blast of flame ripped out almost instantly 
melting a hole through the roof.  He jumped down into it and into 
the building.
